<header class="jumbotron text-center bg-gray-light mb-6 border-bottom px-3">
  <div class="container-lg position-relative">
    <h1 class="alt-h1">Open Source Friday</h1>
    <p class="alt-lead text-gray mb-md-5 col-md-8 mx-auto">Open source is made by people just like you. This week, contribute back to the software you use and love.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container-lg">
<%= render 'layouts/nav' %>
</div>

<div class="container-lg py-2 my-2 px-3">
  <h2 class="alt-h2 text-center">Invest in your future</h2>

  <p class="alt-lead text-gray col-md-10 mx-auto text-center mb-6">
    Open source software is built, well, in the open. Sharpen your skills and be part of something big.
  </p>
  <div class="clearfix gut-lg">
    <div class="float-left col-md-4">
      <div class="clearfix mb-4 text-md-center">
        <div class="float-left mr-4 float-md-none mr-md-0 mb-md-3"><img src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/site/icons/opensource-ico-future.svg?sn" alt="" aria-hidden></div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="alt-h4 mb-2">Shape the future of&nbsp;software</h3>
          <p class="alt-text-small text-gray">Your contributions help make technology better for everyone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="float-left col-md-4">
      <div class="clearfix mb-4 text-md-center">
        <div class="float-left mr-4 float-md-none mr-md-0 mb-md-3"><img src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/site/icons/opensource-ico-best.svg?sn" alt="" aria-hidden></div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="alt-h4 mb-2">Learn from the best in the&nbsp;field</h3>
          <p class="alt-text-small text-gray">Developers of all skill levels participate in open source. Contribute code to projects that run the world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="float-left col-md-4">
      <div class="clearfix mb-4 text-md-center">
        <div class="float-left mr-4 float-md-none mr-md-0 mb-md-3"><img src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/site/icons/opensource-ico-grow.svg?sn" alt="" aria-hidden></div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="alt-h4 mb-2">Grow your skills and help&nbsp;others</h3>
          <p class="alt-text-small text-gray">Whatever your skill level, working on open source software is a great way to learn new&nbsp;things and meet people with similar interests.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-shade-gradient border-top py-6 px-3">
  <div id="participate" class="container-md py-6">

    <h2 class="alt-h2 text-center">Contribute on Open Source Friday</h2>
    <p class="alt-lead text-gray text-center ">Make a plan and stick to it!</p>

    <div class="d-md-table direction-md-rtl my-6 py-6 border-bottom">
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
        <script type="text/javascript">
          (function() {
            if (window.addtocalendar)
              if (typeof window.addtocalendar.start == "function")
                return;
            if (window.ifaddtocalendar == undefined) {
              window.ifaddtocalendar = 1;
              var d = document, s = d.createElement('script'), g = 'getElementsByTagName';
              s.type = 'text/javascript';
              s.charset = 'UTF-8';
              s.async = true;
              s.src = ('https:' == window.location.protocol ? 'https' : 'http') + '://addtocalendar.com/atc/1.5/atc.min.js';
              var h = d[g]('body')[0];
              h.appendChild(s);
            }
          })();
        </script>

        <span class="addtocalendar atc-style-blue">
          <a class="atcb-link btn btn-outline btn-large">
            <%= octicon 'calendar', class: 'mr-2' %>
            Add to Calendar
          </a>

          <var class="atc_event">
              <var class="atc_date_start">2017-05-04 12:00:00</var>
              <var class="atc_date_end">2017-05-04 18:00:00</var>
              <var class="atc_timezone">Europe/London</var>
              <var class="atc_title">Open Source Friday</var>
              <var class="atc_description">Make one contribution to open source today.</var>
              <var class="atc_location">https://ossfriday.com</var>
              <var class="atc_ical_filename">open-source-friday</var>
          </var>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 direction-md-ltr pr-md-6">
        <h3 class="alt-h3">Mark your calendar</h3>

        <p class="text-gray mb-4">
        Set aside two hours per week to work on the open source projects you already use.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-md-table direction-md-ltr my-6 py-6 border-bottom">
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
        <a href="https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/">
          <img class="card img-responsive" src="https://opensource.guide/assets/images/cards/contribute.png">
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 direction-md-ltr pl-md-6">
        <h3 class="alt-h3">Learn to contribute</h3>

        <p class="text-gray mb-4">
          Learn what it means to contribute, and how to find and get started on a new project.
        </p>

        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-outline btn-large" href="https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/">
            <%= octicon 'book', height: 18, class: 'mr-2' %>
            Read the guide
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-bottom">
      <h3 class="alt-h3">Find a project to contribute to</h3>
      <p class="lead text-gray">
        Contributing to open source happens at all levels, across projects. You don’t need to overthink what exactly your first contribution will be, or how it will look.
      </p>
      <div class="d-md-flex gut-md my-6">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="alt-h4 mb-2">A project you already use</h4>
          <p class="text-gray">Start by thinking about the projects you already use or want to use. The projects you’ll actively contribute to are the ones you find yourself coming back to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="alt-h4 mb-2">An issue you can fix</h4>

          <p class="text-gray">Check out these sites to find a project looking for your help:</p>

          <ul class="ml-3">
            <li><a href="http://www.firsttimersonly.com/">First Timers Only</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://yourfirstpr.github.io/">Your First PR</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.codetriage.com/">CodeTriage</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://up-for-grabs.net/">Up For Grabs</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://contributor.ninja">Contributor-ninja</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4 class="alt-h4 mb-2">A warm welcome</h4>

          <p>
            Find a project that has a history and reputation for being welcoming to new contributors in the
            <a href="https://github.com/showcases/great-for-new-contributors">Great for new contributors</a> showcase.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-md-table direction-md-ltr my-6 py-6">
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
        <a href="https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/">
          <img class="img-responsive" src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/site/personal-ill-share.png?sn1">
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 direction-md-ltr pl-md-6">
        <h3 class="alt-h3">Share with the world</h3>

        <p class="text-gray mb-4">
          Work on Open Source Friday with others. When you've made a contribution, share it with the world.
        </p>

        <p>
          <a class="twitter-share-button" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Join%20me%20contributing%20to%20Open%20Source%20Friday" data-size="large">Tweet</a>

          <script>
            window.twttr = (function(d, s, id) {
              var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0], t = window.twttr || {};
              if (d.getElementById(id))
                return t;
              js = d.createElement(s);
              js.id = id;
              js.src = "https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";
              fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);
              t._e = [];
              t.ready = function(f) {
                t._e.push(f);
              };
              return t;
            }(document, "script", "twitter-wjs"));
          </script>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-light border-top py-6 px-3">
  <div class="container-lg">
    <h2 class="alt-h2 mt-6 text-center">You're in good company.</h2>

    <div class="clearfix mt-6 pt-6 mb-4 border-top">
      <div class="col-sm-6 float-left mb-4 mb-md-0 pr-sm-3 pr-lg-4">
        <div>
          <div class="d-table-cell v-align-top pr-3">
            <img src="https://api.adorable.io/avatars/285/ossfriday.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" style="border-radius:25px;">
          </div>
          <blockquote class="d-table-cell v-align-top text-gray">
            <p class="alt-mono-font alt-text-small">“Quote from someone that made their first contribution to open source.”</p>
            <footer class="alt-text-small">Jane Smith, Columbus OH</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 float-left pl-sm-3 pl-lg-4">
        <div>
          <div class="d-table-cell v-align-top pr-3">
            <img src="https://api.adorable.io/avatars/285/ossfriday2.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" style="border-radius:25px;">
          </div>
          <blockquote class="d-table-cell v-align-top text-gray">
            <p class="alt-mono-font alt-text-small">“Another quote that talks about how Open Source Friday saved my life and my dog.”</p>
            <footer class="alt-text-small">Juan Perez, Bogotá Columbia</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-6">
      <div class="clearfix d-md-flex gut-md my-6">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="alt-h3 my-2">
            <a href="/businesses" class="text-blue">Businesses <%= octicon 'chevron-right', height: '26', class: 'text-inherit' %></a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray alt-body-font">Your business runs on open source. Learn how to get involved.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="alt-h3 my-2">
            <a href="/maintainers" class="text-red">Maintainers <%= octicon 'chevron-right', height: '26', class: 'text-inherit' %></a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray alt-body-font">Give your project some love to help others contribute where you need it most.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
